WEBVTT

00:00:29.840 --> 00:00:32.320
we need rapid decarbonization.

00:00:33.240 --> 00:00:35.296
The global carbon budget

00:00:35.320 --> 00:00:38.816
for 66 percent likelihood
to meet the two-degree target

00:00:38.840 --> 00:00:41.480
is approximately 800 gigatons.

00:00:43.640 --> 00:00:46.176
(Laughter)

00:00:46.200 --> 00:00:48.440
OK, now let me try something else.

00:00:49.600 --> 00:00:53.640
We are heading for an uninhabitable earth:

00:00:54.520 --> 00:00:56.616
monster storms,

00:00:56.640 --> 00:00:58.376
killer floods,

00:00:58.400 --> 00:01:00.696
devastating wildfires,